Package jcuda.jcusparse Description

Contains the classes of JCusparse.

This package contains classes that are related to JCusparse. The main class is the JCusparse class, which provides all method bindings for CUSPARSE, the NVIDIA CUDA sparse matrix library.

Please consult your CUSPARSE library documentation for more information about how to use this API.
